{"comments":"Voice compounds — higher-level compositions for AI voice personas.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nThese compounds compose atoms from Voice, Formant, and Speech modules into\ncomplete voice \"characters\" that agents can embody. At billion-agent scale,\ndeterministic voice identity enables:\n\n- Consistent brand voice across all agent interactions\n- Voice personas that persist across sessions\n- Emotional modulation without losing identity\n- Multi-voice dialogues with clear speaker distinction\n\n## VoiceCharacter\nA complete voice identity including physical characteristics (pitch, formants),\nspeaking style (rate, articulation), and emotional baseline.\n\n## SpeechPattern\nRhythmic and stylistic patterns that characterize how a voice speaks:\npausing habits, emphasis patterns, filler usage.\n\n## Dialogue\nMulti-turn conversational structures with speaker attribution and timing.\n\n## Usage\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Schema.Audio.VoiceCompounds as VC\n\n-- Define a friendly assistant voice\nassistantVoice = VC.voiceCharacter\n  \"Aria\"\n  VC.PersonaFriendly\n  (Voice.voiceProfile Voice.pitchMedium Voice.rateNormal ...)\n  (Formant.formantSetFromVowel Formant.VowelSchwa)\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[121,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/VoiceCompounds.purs","start":[121,3]},"title":"PersonaNeutral"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[122,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/VoiceCompounds.purs","start":[122,3]},"title":"PersonaFriendly"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[123,25],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/VoiceCompounds.purs","start":[123,3]},"title":"PersonaAuthoritative"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[124,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/VoiceCompounds.purs","start":[124,3]},"title":"PersonaCalm"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[125,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/VoiceCompounds.purs","start":[125,3]},"title":"PersonaEnergetic"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[126,22],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/VoiceCompounds.purs","start":[126,3]},"title":"PersonaThoughtful"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[127,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/VoiceCompounds.purs","start":[127,3]},"title":"PersonaPlayful"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[128,22],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/VoiceCompounds.purs","start":[128,3]},"title":"PersonaEmpathetic"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Audio","VoiceCompounds"],"Persona"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[130,40],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/VoiceCompounds.purs","start":[130,1]},"title":"eqPersona"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Audio","VoiceCompounds"],"Persona"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[131,42],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio/VoiceCompounds.purs","start":[131,1]},"title":"ordPersona"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag"